Package: idschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Idaho School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Idaho State Department
    of Education (SDE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment data from the
    SDE's public finance portal and transforming it into tidy format for analysis.
    Supports historical enrollment data by district, charter school, and building.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    readxl,
    readr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    rlang,
    httr,
    rappdirs
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    scales
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://almartin82.github.io/idschooldata, https://github.com/almartin82/idschooldata
BugReports: https://github.com/almartin82/idschooldata/issues
